Package: cod
Title: CodSpeed Benchmark Harness for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Davis", "Vaughan", , "davis@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("CodSpeed Technology SAS", role = "cph",
           comment = "Author of the vendored instrument-hooks library"),
    person("Posit Software, PBC", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Instruments R expressions with CodSpeed's instrument-hooks C
    library so that benchmark results are recorded when an R process is run
    under the CodSpeed runner. Provides a thin binding layer over the
    instrument-hooks C API and a high-level 'test()' interface for writing
    benchmarks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/r-lib/cod
BugReports: https://github.com/r-lib/cod/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    rlang (>= 1.1.0),
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/build/compilation-database: true
Config/testthat/edition: 3
